LilycoveCity_House2_EventScript_FatMan_Text_1:
	.string "Zzz… Hm?\nTake this, too?$"

LilycoveCity_House2_EventScript_FatMan_Text_2:
	.string "Zzz…\nHm? Wha--?\pLemme be… I'm still half-asleep…\nHere… Just take this…$"

